{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Accessibility","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Glossary/Accessibility","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Web Accessibility</em> (<strong>A11Y</strong>) ist ein Begriff, der empfohlene Methoden beschreibt, um eine Website für Menschen mit physischen und technischen Einschränkungen zugänglich zu machen.&nbsp;Web accessibility wird am <a href=\"/de/docs/Glossary/W3C\">W3C</a> durch die <a href=\"/de/docs/Glossary/WAI\">Web Accessibility Initiative</a> (WAI) definiert und diskutiert.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"mehr_erfahren","title":"Mehr erfahren","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"allgemeines","title":"Allgemeines","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/Accessibility\">Accessibility resources at MDN</a></li>\n <li><a title=\"Web accessibility\" href=\"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Web_accessibility\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web accessibility</a> auf Wikipedia</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"lernmaterial","title":"Lernmaterial","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://webaim.org/\" rel=\"external noopener\" class=\"external\">Web Accessibility In Mind</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"technische_referenz","title":"Technische Referenz","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA\">The ARIA documentation on MDN</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/WAI/\" rel=\"external noopener\" class=\"external\">The Web Accessibility Initiative homepage</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/wai-aria/\" rel=\"external noopener\" class=\"external\">The WAI-ARIA recommendation</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Mehr erfahren","id":"mehr_erfahren"}],"summary":"Web Accessibility (A11Y) ist ein Begriff, der empfohlene Methoden beschreibt, um eine Website für Menschen mit physischen und technischen Einschränkungen zugänglich zu machen. Web accessibility wird am W3C durch die Web Accessibility Initiative (WAI) definiert und diskutiert.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Accessibility","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Accesibilidad","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Accessibilité","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Accessibility (アクセシビリティ)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"접근성","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Accessibility","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Acessibilidade","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Доступность","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Accessibility","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Accessibility","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/glossary/accessibility","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/glossary/accessibility/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Glossary","title":"Glossar"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Glossary/Accessibility","title":"Accessibility"}],"pageTitle":"Accessibility - Glossar | MDN","noIndexing":false}}